{"tid":1704394,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（抵制TVB）賽馬會贊助CCTVB節目 沈迷賭博倒錢落海","createTime":"2019-11-10T16:21:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-11T14:57:35.000Z","uid":75759,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a57a4e8636816836fa14e0a8bff8f150504d1c1a","tid":1704394,"uid":75759,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:21:13.000Z","msg":"各位marketing JJ注意，<br />\nTVB係<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">品牌負資產</span></span></strong>，喺TVB落廣告，<br />\n你哋苦心經營嘅<strong><span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">品牌形象將付諸流水</span></span></strong>！無人可憐！<img src=\"/assets/faces/husky/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nTVB今個月開始同廣告客戶傾下年合約，Keep住個氣勢到年底啦！<br />\n廣告界多番強調，去FB洗版係有用ga<br />\n<br />\n是晚重溫@10 Nov 2019 <br />\n香港賽馬會<br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/TheHongKongJockeyClub\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FTheHongKongJockeyClub&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=643f4119\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/TheHongKongJockeyClub</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://facebook.com/HKJCRacing\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffacebook.com%2FHKJCRacing&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=44f72f55\" target=\"_blank\">https://facebook.com/HKJCRacing</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/XL5Fkyb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXL5Fkyb.jpg&h=3365f654&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【賽馬會做咩？】<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">贊助CCTVB節目</span></span></strong><br />\n有巴打報料話無綫新聞台及財經台嘅節目<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">冠名贊助</span></strong>（例如83台節目「運動大本營」）係新聞部高層<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黃淑明</span></strong>同<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">袁志偉</span></strong>傾返嚟，佢哋靠撈呢啲油水穩定自己地位。<br />\nSource：樓豬<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">博彩稅送錢俾777買化武毒害市民</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong>馬會上年度博彩投注額2475億元創新高　破紀錄繳稅233億</strong><br />\n<pre><code data-type=\"\">下周日(9月1日)新馬季開鑼，香港賽馬會今晚（28日）公布2018/2019財政年度(由2018年7月1日至2019年6月30日)賽馬、足智彩及六合彩總投注額，錄得破紀錄的2,475億元，升5.8%；為庫房帶來破紀錄的233億元博彩稅及利得稅收益，佔稅務局稅收總額6.8%；同時慈善捐款再次刷新紀錄，達43億元。</code></pre><br />\nSource：HK01<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"><strong><del>dklm買六合彩$40都未中過</del></strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">再唔撤budget，業績定仆直！<br />\n盡快同TVB割席！</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n【抵制CCTVB 任務流程】<br />\n基本：<br />\n1.派嬲 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n2.洗版 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n3.罷買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n進階：<br />\n4. 放張抵制圖留言以示不滿<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n5.負評 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/beg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />請用幾秒去派嬲、留言、推post <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />俾幾秒我哋抵制TVB團隊得唔得? <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n※請善用template，清晰表達訴求<br />\n無綫新聞，歪曲事實，出賣港人！本人明白貴公司或已簽訂今年合約，未能即時撤回廣告，故暫時罷用。請貴公司承諾不簽訂2020 TVB廣告合約，不以無綫藝人代言，否則將列入「永久抵制名單」，永不錄用。<br />\n<br />\n記得bookmark: TVB廣告客戶名單！！ <br />\n消費前諗清楚 <br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2P7cPeD&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=b810722a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2P7cPeD</a> <br />\n－－－－－－－ <br />\n請即follow: <br />\nFB: <a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fsayno2tvb&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=81aac193\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nIG: #sayno2tvb<br />\nTG 綜合狙擊頻道（已被封<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=8fb1f1a1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb</a><br />\nTG 繼續狙擊頻道（新channel，請follow）: <a href=\"https://t.me/sayno2tvb2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fsayno2tvb2&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=e5e375aa\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/sayno2tvb2</a><br />\nTG CCTVB記者實時位置狙擊頻道: <a href=\"https://t.me/nomoretvb\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fnomoretvb&d=%2FSZuxPcvMLfRWwfRMm0dxPo5m3Xr9SEp5dZU2qkndIk%3D&h=dfcac632\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/nomoretvb</a><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">多謝大家</span></span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5971bb4b1ef4f24e1d626b1bb501bc068a845aa","tid":1704394,"uid":4174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"其實CCTVB 冇晒本地商業廣告<br />\n淨係靠馬會 政府 大陸廣告商維唔維到皮"},{"pid":"5bdbbf6893a1381a0b8e24450352d67669753d50","tid":1704394,"uid":38757,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"c5971bb4b1ef4f24e1d626b1bb501bc068a845aa","tid":1704394,"uid":4174,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:24:11.000Z","msg":"其實CCTVB 冇晒本地商業廣告<br />\n淨係靠馬會 政府 大陸廣告商維唔維到皮"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-10T16:35:38.000Z","msg":"呢個真係唔知了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢依家真係同以前廣告數量少左一半<br />\n黃女時間都係得四到五個廣告 好有以前atv未期味道<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgm